primary_asset_contracts.name: Daz3D Non-Fungible People
primary_asset_contracts.description:
Daz 3D’s debut NFT collection, Non-Fungible People (NFP), is a collection of 8,888 hyper-realistic 3D Avatars.  Each NFP comes with a fully rigged 3D model and a PFP rendered in breathtaking 3D.  Use your NFP for video calls, motion capture, game design, animation and more!

You can even upgrade your NFP with a new wearable from the [Champion x NFP Collection](https://opensea.io/collection/champion-x-non-fungible-people)

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/non-fungible-people and check out the Official Non-Fungible People website https://nfp.daz3d.com

License: All NFP’s come with the Daz 3D interactive license found here: https://www.daz3d.com/eula
